ke":1,"score":-1,"citedBy":1,"replyTime":"2018-10-09T09:50:17.000Z","msg":"咪玩啦<br />\n就算支那抄足100%<br />\n你韓國都有80%啦"},{"pid":"cd54ffdc978050a84af5734128b5a17a49c9f023","tid":854012,"uid":67294,"like":0,"dislike":0,"score":0,"quote":{"pid":"9a4a5003ca8d4263a2135a6e7aa8b224a59762b9","tid":854012,"uid":41245,"like":0,"dislike":1,"score":-1,"citedBy":1,"replyTime":"2018-10-09T09:50:17.000Z","msg":"咪玩啦<br />\n就算支那抄足100%<br />\n你韓國都有80%啦"},"citedBy":0,"replyTime":"2018-10-09T15:18:49.000Z","msg":"經典running man抄全員逃走中<img src=\"/assets/faces/dog/smile.gif\" class=\"hkgmoji\" /> <br />\n抄到話自己國民綜藝<img src=\"/assets/faces/dog/haha.gif\" class=\"hkgmoji\" /> <img src=\"/assets/faces/dog/haha.gif\" class=\"hkgmoji\" />"},{"pid":"f71f0c6f2cc23a849bc7701b46083d140a9fa90f","tid":854012,"uid":67294,"like":0,"dislike":0,"score":0,"quote":{"pid":"90080b98612666337a74d6a4a86cb161cbcd7110","tid":854012,"uid":173083,"like":24,"dislike":0,"score":24,"quote":{"pid":"66f3951883efd531c59d0ff49e82f27052efdcdc","tid":854012,"uid":67294,"like":5,"dislike":22,"score":-17,"citedBy":3,"replyTime":"2018-10-09T05:08:21.000Z","msg":"好聲音 爸爸去哪兒 我是歌手 創造101全部有買弗水權<br />\n垃圾記者又呃稿費"},"citedBy":1,"replyTime":"2018-10-09T05:12:39.000Z","msg":"中國好聲音係有買、咁中國新歌聲呢？<br />\n<br />\n買咗兩年學鳩哂人地啲嘢之後第三年整舊一撚樣嘅出嚟<br />\n<br />\n枉你仲好意思講"},"citedBy":0,"replyTime":"2018-10-09T15:22:12.000Z","msg":"事實上好多王牌綜藝都係有版權<br />\n依家個記者唔分清楚誤導讀者全部都係抄有無職業操守<img src=\"/assets/faces/normal/wonder.gif\" class=\"hkgmoji\" />"}]}